     "attributes": {
      "body": "Welcome to Men's Wellness Centers, {{contact.first_name}} your membership is officially active\n\nYour home center: {{custom_values.newport_news__address}} Hours: {{custom_values.newport_news__hours}} \n\nQuestions anytime: just reply here or call (757) 806-6263. \n\nWe're glad you're with us.\nReply STOP to opt out.",
