     "order": 2,
     "attributes": {
      "subject": "Your first visit at Men's Wellness Centers, what to know",
      "html": "<p style=\"margin:0px;font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size:16px; padding-left: 0px!important;margin: 0px;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;font-size: 16px;\">Hi {{contact.first_name}}, Welcome again, here's everything you need for a smooth first visit. <br><br>WHERE Men's Wellness Centers – Newport News {{custom_values.newport_news__address}} Free parking is available on-site. WHEN YOU ARRIVE Come in about 10 minutes early. <br><br>Check in at the front desk the team will already have you on the schedule.<br><br>WHAT TO BRING <br>- A photo ID <br>- Your current medication list, if any <br>- Any questions you've been holding onto visits are unhurried on purpose WHO YOU'LL MEET Your Patient Care Consultant will walk you through your membership and your schedule going forward, and the clinical team takes it from there. <br><br>Need to adjust anything before then? <br>Reply to this email or call us at (757) 806-6263. <br><br>See you soon, <br>The Men's Wellness Centers Team – Newport News</p>",
